com.hesamian.ring

Class Ring

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hesamian.ring.Ring

  • public class Ring
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles Polynomial ring. Ring is a combination of Monomials, Operations and even nested Rings.
    Since:
    08/30/2016
    Author:
    Seyedamirhossein Hesamian

      • replaceVariables

        public Ring replaceVariables(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> map)
        This method gets as argument Map and it will loop through the Ring and replace old variables with new one. For example: x -> y. Avoid over complicating or misusing this method. For instance replacing x -> y^2 will result in: 2x^3 -> 2y^2^3 which is invalid. This method supports method chaining.
        Parameters:
        Map -
        Returns:
        Ring
